<br>
It was a long walk, but at the end of it Schaard  Ob'Tenebrae came upon scrolls without number.  The memoirs of Krintek K'kidrak.  Here Schaard would sit.  Here he would learn from his master.  Here he would prepare for the next world, ... perhaps even this one. <p>       <i>"I do not call cold-spirited, mulish, blind, or intoxicated men stout-hearted.  He possesses heart who knows fear but <b>masters</b> fear; who sees the abyss, but sees it with <b>pride</b>.<br>
       He who sees the abyss, but with an eagle's eyes - he who <b>grasps</b> the abyss but with an eagle's claws: <b>he</b> possesses courage." </i></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub73.ezboard.com/fshadowguardsullonzekfrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=89.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fshadowguardsullonzekfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.shadowguard.org/resources/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fshadowguardsullonzekfrm4.threadControl?topicID=89.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fshadowguardsullonzekfrm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=89.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fshadowguardsullonzekfrm4.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=89.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub73.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="shadowguardsullonzekfrm0">The Moat (Public OOC Board)<option value="shadowguardsullonzekfrm4">The Tavern (Public In-Character)<option value="shadowguardsullonzekfrm19">The Gate (Membership Applications)<option value="shadowguardsullonzekfrm12">The Bazaar (Trade Board)<option value="shadowguardsullonzekfrm14">The Blighted Garden (Allied IC Board)<option value="shadowguardsullonzekfrm10">The Council Chambers (Alliance Discussions)<option value="